FBIS3-23118 "jptot010__l94081" JPRS-TOT-94-010-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 10 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Update on, Reactions to Hebron Mosque Massacre Jihad Promises Revenge Within Day NC2602134094 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain in Arabic 1230 GMT 26 Feb 94 NC2602134094 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The Islamic Jihad Organization in Palestine has announced that it will begin mounting acts of revenge and retaliation because of the massacre. The group issued a statement saying that the Palestine Liberation Battalions [kata'ib tahrir filastin] and the Jihad Eagles Group [majmu'at nusur al-jihad] have been placed on a state of maximum alert. The statement adds: We vow that in less than 24 hours these groups will have begun taking revenge upon the enemy inside and outside the occupied territories.
